data.description: This is the perfect starter home in unincorporated O'Fallon in the Ft. Zumwalt school district!  The 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home was designed with family in mind and waiting for your finishing touches.  The large deck out back is perfect for weekend BBQs or evening drinks with friends!  With a large, oversized, 3-car garage, along with room for a car lift, the garage is sure to impress the auto aficionado!  Make your appointment today and don't miss out on this one!
